-- Camiro Says Posadas to Cut Debt Ratio by Half This Year
-- B y
-- 2012-04-14T16:27:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-14/camiro-says-posadas-to-cut-debt-ratio-by-half-this-year-video-.html
Ruben Camiro, chief financial 
officer of  Mexico 's Grupo Posadas SAB, talks about the state of 
the hotel industry, the outlook for the company's growth and 
profitability, and the debt renegotiation strategy of Latin 
America's largest hotel chain operator.  The company aims to cut a measure of indebtedness by half 
this year as it sells assets to help meet obligations over the 
next three years. Camiro spoke with Bloomberg's Benjamin Bain in
Mexico City yesterday. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 15:53
 